snippet.title: BREAKING: Brian Laundrie Died by Suicide, Medical Examiner Says #HeyJB #WFLANow
snippet.description: #BREAKING: BRIAN LAUNDRIE'S DEATH RULED A SUICIDE, ATTORNEY SAYS | Brian Laundrie, the person of interest in Gabby Petito's homicide, died by gunshot wound to the head and his manner of death has been ruled a suicide, according to Laundrie family attorney Steven Bertolino. WFLA Now's JB Biunno and Josh Benson are live on #WFLANow with the latest. bit.ly/3l5txZt
